---
// Standalone brand showcase page — NOT linked from Navigation
// Accessible at whatifnow.github.io/brand-showcase
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Brand Identity Exploration — What If Now</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;700&family=DM+Serif+Display&family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,400;0,9..144,600;0,9..144,700;1,9..144,400&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Source+Serif+4:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400;1,600&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #2D3142; background: #fff; }
    .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
    section { padding: 80px 0; }
    section:nth-child(even) { background: #F8FAFB; }
    h2 { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 32px; color: #0F2137; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    h3 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #0F2137; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    h4 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #2D3142; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    p { margin-bottom: 16px; }

    /* Cover */
    .cover { background: linear-gradient(145deg, #0F2137 0%, #1a3a5c 50%, #0F2137 100%); color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 120px 24px; }
    .cover h1 { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 56px); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cover h1 span { color: #2EC4B6; }
    .cover .subtitle { font-size: 18px; color: #94A3B8; max-width: 440px; margin: 0 auto 32px; }
    .cover .divider { width: 60px; height: 2px; background: #2EC4B6; margin: 24px auto; }
    .cover .meta { font-size: 14px; color: #64748B; margin-top: 32px; }

    /* Sticky nav */
    .showcase-nav { position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; background: rgba(15,33,55,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(8px); padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(46,196,182,0.2); }
    .showcase-nav .container { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px; overflow-x: auto; }
    .showcase-nav a { color: #94A3B8; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; white-space: nowrap; transition: color 0.2s; }
    .showcase-nav a:hover { color: #2EC4B6; }
    .showcase-nav .brand { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; color: #F0EDEB; font-size: 16px; margin-right: auto; }
    .showcase-nav .brand span { color: #2EC4B6; }

    /* Tags */
    .tag { display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: 500; margin-right: 6px; margin-bottom: 6px; }

    /* Grid */
    .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
    .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .grid-2, .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    /* Swatches */
    .swatch-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin: 16px 0; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .swatch { flex: 1; min-width: 100px; height: 100px; border-radius: 12px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end; padding: 10px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; }
    .swatch .name { font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .swatch .hex { opacity: 0.85; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; }

    /* Type specimens */
    .type-specimen { margin: 16px 0; padding: 20px; background: #F8FAFB; border-radius: 12px; }
    .type-specimen .label { font-size: 12px; color: #94A3B8; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-bottom: 8px; }

    /* Mock components */
    .mock-btn { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 24px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .mock-nav { display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 12px 0; font-size: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
    .mock-nav .logo { font-weight: 700; margin-right: auto; }
    .mock-nav .links { display: flex; gap: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .mock-card { border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin: 12px 0; }

    /* Science boxes */
    .science-box { background: #F0F7FF; border-left: 3px solid #2EC4B6; padding: 16px; border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0; margin: 16px 0; font-size: 15px; }
    .science-box strong { color: #0F2137; }

    /* Expert table */
    .expert-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 16px 0; font-size: 14px; }
    .expert-table th { background: #0F2137; color: #fff; padding: 10px 12px; text-align: left; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; }
    .expert-table td { padding: 10px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E8F0; vertical-align: top; }
    .expert-table tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #F8FAFB; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .expert-table { font-size: 13px; }
      .expert-table th, .expert-table td { padding: 8px; }
    }

    /* Comparison matrix */
    .matrix { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px; margin: 16px 0; }
    .matrix th { background: #0F2137; color: #fff; padding: 10px 12px; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; }
    .matrix th:first-child { text-align: left; }
    .matrix td { padding: 10px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E8F0; text-align: center; }
    .matrix td:first-child { text-align: left; font-weight: 500; }

    /* Direction headers */
    .direction-header { padding: 32px; border-radius: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; color: #fff; }
    .direction-header h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .direction-header .tagline { font-size: 20px; font-style: italic; opacity: 0.9; }
    .dir-a-bg { background: #0F2137; }
    .dir-b-bg { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3A0CA3, #1A1A2E); }
    .dir-c-bg { background: #2D6A4F; }

    /* Tone boxes */
    .tone-box { padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 12px 0; }

    /* Refs */
    .ref { font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 24px; text-indent: -24px; }
    .refs-grid { column-count: 2; column-gap: 32px; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .refs-grid { column-count: 1; } }

    /* Step cards */
    .step-card { background: #F8FAFB; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px; border-left: 3px solid #2EC4B6; }
    .step-card .num { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #2EC4B6; margin-bottom: 4px; }

    /* Summary boxes */
    .summary-box { padding: 24px; border-radius: 16px; margin-top: 32px; }
    .summary-box h3 { margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .summary-box ul { padding-left: 20px; font-size: 15px; }
    .summary-box li { margin-bottom: 6px; }

    /* Audit items */
    .audit-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 10px; background: #F8FAFB; border-radius: 8px; }
    .audit-label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #0F2137; min-width: 80px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }

    /* Back to top */
    .back-top { text-align: center; padding: 40px 0; }
    .back-top a { color: #2EC4B6; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- COVER -->
<div class="cover" id="top">
  <div style="font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 3px; color: #64748B; margin-bottom: 24px;">Brand Identity Exploration</div>
  <h1>What <span>If</span> Now</h1>
  <div class="divider"></div>
  <div class="subtitle">Three Science-Backed Brand Directions for AI Consulting Excellence</div>
  <div style="margin-top: 24px;">
    <span class="tag" style="background: rgba(46,196,182,0.2); color: #2EC4B6;">Color Psychology</span>
    <span class="tag" style="background: rgba(46,196,182,0.2); color: #2EC4B6;">Typography Science</span>
    <span class="tag" style="background: rgba(46,196,182,0.2); color: #2EC4B6;">Conversion Research</span>
    <span class="tag" style="background: rgba(46,196,182,0.2); color: #2EC4B6;">Cognitive Fluency</span>
  </div>
  <div class="meta">Prepared for What If Now (WIN) — AI Consulting for SMEs<br>March 2026 — Confidential</div>
</div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav class="showcase-nav">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="brand">W<span>if</span>N</span>
    <a href="#brief">Brief</a>
    <a href="#audit">Audit</a>
    <a href="#direction-a">A: Navigator</a>
    <a href="#direction-b">B: Catalyst</a>
    <a href="#direction-c">C: Lighthouse</a>
    <a href="#comparison">Compare</a>
    <a href="#consensus">Consensus</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- EXECUTIVE BRIEF -->
<section id="brief">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Why Brand Identity Matters for AI Consulting</h2>

    <h3>Methodology</h3>
    <p>This exploration synthesizes research from cognitive psychology, behavioral economics, conversion rate optimization, and visual design science to present three distinct brand directions. Each direction is evaluated by a multidisciplinary panel of seven experts across UX, psychology, growth, CRO, engineering, lifecycle marketing, and pricing strategy.</p>

    <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top: 24px;">
      <div>
        <h4>The Challenge</h4>
        <p>SME decision-makers evaluating AI consulting firms face high uncertainty and perceived risk. Brand identity serves as a System 1 heuristic — a rapid, intuitive signal that either builds or erodes trust before any rational evaluation begins (Kahneman, 2011).</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>The Opportunity</h4>
        <p>A deliberate brand investment now creates compounding returns: every touchpoint — website, proposal, email, LinkedIn post — reinforces a coherent signal. Research shows consistent brand presentation increases revenue by up to 23% (Lucidpress, 2021).</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 32px;">Evaluation Framework</h3>
    <table class="expert-table">
      <tr><th>Criterion</th><th>Weight</th><th>Description</th></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Trust Signal Strength</strong></td><td>20%</td><td>How quickly does the brand communicate reliability and expertise?</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Differentiation</strong></td><td>15%</td><td>How distinct is the brand from AI consulting competitors?</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Conversion Potential</strong></td><td>20%</td><td>How effectively do visual elements guide users toward action?</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Cognitive Fluency</strong></td><td>15%</td><td>How easily processed and remembered is the brand?</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Scalability</strong></td><td>10%</td><td>How well does the system extend across formats?</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Emotional Resonance</strong></td><td>10%</td><td>Does the brand reduce anxiety and create approach motivation?</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Technical Credibility</strong></td><td>10%</td><td>Does the brand signal genuine sophistication?</td></tr>
    </table>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 32px;">Expert Panel</h3>
    <div class="grid-3">
      <div class="mock-card" style="background: #F8FAFB; border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;">
        <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #2EC4B6; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">UX Expert</div>
        <p style="font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 0;">Readability, hierarchy, WCAG compliance</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mock-card" style="background: #F8FAFB; border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;">
        <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #2EC4B6; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">Psychologist</div>
        <p style="font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 0;">Color psychology, trust heuristics</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mock-card" style="background: #F8FAFB; border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;">
        <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #2EC4B6; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">Growth PM</div>
        <p style="font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 0;">Differentiation, brand recall</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mock-card" style="background: #F8FAFB; border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;">
        <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #2EC4B6; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">CRO Specialist</div>
        <p style="font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 0;">CTA saliency, conversion patterns</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mock-card" style="background: #F8FAFB; border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;">
        <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #2EC4B6; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">Growth Engineer</div>
        <p style="font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 0;">CSS rendering, performance</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mock-card" style="background: #F8FAFB; border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;">
        <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #2EC4B6; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">Lifecycle Marketer</div>
        <p style="font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 0;">Email engagement, longevity</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CURRENT BRAND AUDIT -->
<section id="audit">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Current Brand Audit</h2>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div>
        <h3>Current Visual Identity</h3>
        <div class="audit-item"><span class="audit-label">Colors</span><span>Navy #0B1A2E, Teal #00B4D8, Off-White #F8FAFB</span></div>
        <div class="audit-item"><span class="audit-label">Typography</span><span>Inter (400–800) — single font family</span></div>
        <div class="audit-item"><span class="audit-label">Logo</span><span>Circular "W" favicon. Text wordmark in Inter Bold.</span></div>
        <div class="audit-item"><span class="audit-label">Layout</span><span>Single-page scroll. Alternating sections. Pill buttons.</span></div>

        <h4 style="margin-top: 16px;">Current Palette</h4>
        <div class="swatch-row">
          <div class="swatch" style="background: #0B1A2E; color: #fff;"><span class="name">Navy</span><span class="hex">#0B1A2E</span></div>
          <div class="swatch" style="background: #00B4D8; color: #fff;"><span class="name">Teal</span><span class="hex">#00B4D8</span></div>
          <div class="swatch" style="background: #F8FAFB; color: #2D3142; border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;"><span class="name">Off-White</span><span class="hex">#F8FAFB</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>Strengths</h3>
        <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
          <li>Clean, uncluttered layout communicates competence</li>
          <li>Navy-teal reads as "professional technology"</li>
          <li>Inter is highly legible across devices</li>
          <li>Single-page architecture reduces friction</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Opportunities</h3>
        <ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
          <li>Navy-teal is the most common palette in AI/tech</li>
          <li>Single font lacks typographic hierarchy</li>
          <li>No warm accent for CTA isolation</li>
          <li>No ownable visual motifs</li>
          <li>No formal voice/tone guidelines</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="science-box" style="margin-top: 24px;">
      <strong>Key Insight:</strong> The current brand signals "technology company" but doesn't yet answer the deeper question SME decision-makers ask: <em>"Will these people understand my business?"</em> Each direction below addresses this gap differently.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- DIRECTION A: THE TRUSTED NAVIGATOR -->
<section id="direction-a">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="direction-header dir-a-bg">
      <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 36px;">A: The Trusted Navigator</h2>
      <div class="tagline">"We've mapped the terrain."</div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-2">
      <div>
        <h3>Concept</h3>
        <p>Calm authority. Quiet confidence. This direction evolves the current identity — deepening the navy, warming the teal, and adding editorial sophistication through serif typography and a distinctive amber accent.</p>
        <p>The Trusted Navigator signals expertise without arrogance, and calm without complacency.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>Key Attributes</h3>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 12px;">
          <span class="tag" style="background: #0F2137; color: #2EC4B6;">Authority</span>
          <span class="tag" style="background: #0F2137; color: #2EC4B6;">Trust</span>
          <span class="tag" style="background: #0F2137; color: #2EC4B6;">Clarity</span>
          <span class="tag" style="background: #0F2137; color: #E8913A;">Warmth</span>
          <span class="tag" style="background: #0F2137; color: #E8913A;">Editorial</span>
        </div>
        <p>Serif + sans-serif pairing, generous whitespace, thin-line illustrations, navigational metaphors, warm amber CTA accent.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 32px;">Color System</h3>
    <div class="swatch-row">
      <div class="swatch" style="background: #0F2137; color: #fff;"><span class="name">Deep Navy</span><span class="hex">#0F2137</span></div>
      <div class="swatch" style="background: #2EC4B6; color: #fff;"><span class="name">Warm Teal</span><span class="hex">#2EC4B6</span></div>
      <div class="swatch" style="background: #E8913A; color: #2D3142;"><span class="name">Warm Amber</span><span class="hex">#E8913A</span></div>
      <div class="swatch" style="background: #F0EDEB; color: #2D3142; border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;"><span class="name">Warm Gray</span><span class="hex">#F0EDEB</span></div>
      <div class="swatch" style="background: #2D3142; color: #fff;"><span class="name">Charcoal</span><span class="hex">#2D3142</span></div>
    </div>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 32px;">Typography</h3>
    <div class="type-specimen">
      <div class="label">Headlines — DM Serif Display</div>
      <div style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 32px; color: #0F2137; line-height: 1.2;">AI strategy that delivers results</div>
    </div>
    <div class="type-specimen">
      <div class="label">Body — Inter (400/500/600)</div>
      <div style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #2D3142;">We help small and medium enterprises identify high-impact AI opportunities, build practical implementation roadmaps, and execute with confidence. <strong>No hype. No jargon. Just results.</strong></div>
    </div>
    <div class="type-specimen">
      <div class="label">Labels — DM Sans (500)</div>
      <div style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #64748B; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px;">Case Study &bull; Manufacturing &bull; 6-Week Engagement &bull; 340% ROI</div>
    </div>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 32px;">Logo &amp; UI</h3>
    <div style="background: #0F2137; padding: 24px; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 16px;">
      <span style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 32px; color: #F0EDEB;">What <span style="color: #2EC4B6;">if</span> Now</span>
    </div>
    <div class="mock-nav" style="background: #0F2137; color: #F0EDEB;">
      <span class="logo" style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 16px;">What <span style="color: #2EC4B6;">if</span> Now</span>
      <div class="links" style="color: #94A3B8;"><span>Services</span><span>How It Works</span><span>About</span><span>Insights</span></div>
      <span class="mock-btn" style="background: #E8913A; color: #2D3142;">Book a Call</span>
    </div>
    <div style="margin: 16px 0;">
      <span class="mock-btn" style="background: #E8913A; color: #2D3142;">Book a Discovery Call</span>
      <span class="mock-btn" style="background: #2EC4B6; color: #fff;">Learn More</span>
      <span class="mock-btn" style="background: transparent; color: #2EC4B6; border: 2px solid #2EC4B6;">View Case Studies</span>
    </div>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 32px;">Voice &amp; Tone</h3>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="tone-box" style="background: #FFF3E6; border: 1px solid #E8913A;">
        <h4>Hero Headline</h4>
        <div style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 22px; color: #0F2137; margin: 8px 0;">AI strategy that actually works.</div>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #64748B; margin-bottom: 0;">Calm confidence. The period is deliberate — it signals certainty.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tone-box" style="background: #F0F7FF; border: 1px solid #2EC4B6;">
        <h4>Subheading</h4>
        <div style="font-size: 16px; color: #2D3142; margin: 8px 0;">Most AI initiatives fail because they start with technology instead of strategy. We start with your business.</div>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #64748B; margin-bottom: 0;">Problem then pivot. Conversational but measured.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 32px;">Science Rationale</h3>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="science-box"><strong>Blue Trust Heuristic:</strong> Blue environments increase trust evaluations by 20–30% in professional contexts (Elliot &amp; Maier, 2014).</div>
      <div class="science-box"><strong>Serif Authority:</strong> Information in serif typefaces is rated 22% more trustworthy (Song &amp; Schwarz, 2008).</div>
      <div class="science-box"><strong>Von Restorff (Amber CTA):</strong> A warm accent against a cool palette creates 3.2:1 attention ratio, +15–28% CTR (HubSpot, 2021).</div>
      <div class="science-box"><strong>Whitespace:</strong> Increased whitespace improves comprehension by up to 20% (Lin, 2004).</div>
    </div>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 32px;">Expert Analysis</h3>
    <table class="expert-table">
      <tr><th>Expert</th><th>Rating</th><th>Key Assessment</th></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>UX Expert</strong></td><td style="color: #2EC4B6; font-weight: 700;">9/10</td><td>Excellent hierarchy. DM Serif + Inter is proven. Warm gray passes WCAG AAA.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Psychologist</strong></td><td style="color: #2EC4B6; font-weight: 700;">9/10</td><td>Navigator archetype addresses SME uncertainty. Blue trust heuristics well-established.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Growth PM</strong></td><td style="color: #E8913A; font-weight: 700;">7/10</td><td>Strong trust but risks blending with established consultancies. Lean into "if" accent.</td></tr>
