    <div class="science-box" style="margin-top: 16px;">
      <strong>Key Takeaway:</strong> Directions A and C are statistically tied. A optimizes for <em>trust and conversion</em>. C optimizes for <em>differentiation and emotional resonance</em>. B excels at <em>differentiation and technical credibility</em> but carries highest implementation complexity.
